---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | shanmuganand.m" description="My background, skills, and approach to software engineering.">
  <main class="main-content page-transition">
    <!-- Inline Nav -->
    <div class="nav-links inline-nav">
      <a href="/" class="cmd-link">[ ← cd ~ ]</a>
    </div>

    <Section id="about-full" title="about">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>I am a Senior Frontend Engineer with over 5 years of experience building scalable web applications. My journey started with WordPress and jQuery, evolved through React and Next.js, and has arrived at a strong preference for web fundamentals over heavy framework abstractions.</p>
        
        <p>Currently, I split my time between modernizing legacy codebases, designing robust component libraries, and integrating LLMs into user-facing products. I believe that good engineering is about making tradeoffs explicit and writing code that is easy to delete.</p>

        <h3>Focus Areas</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Design Systems:</strong> Translating Figma tokens into resilient CSS/Tailwind architectures without relying on third-party UI libraries when possible.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Achieving perfect Core Web Vitals scores by shipping less JavaScript, lazy-loading resources, and optimizing the critical rendering path.</li>
          <li><strong>Developer Experience:</strong> Standardizing linting, CI/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions), and local development environments to accelerate team velocity.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Work Authorization</h3>
        <p>I am a <strong>U.S. Permanent Resident (Green Card holder)</strong> and do not require sponsorship to work in the United States.</p>
        <h3>Languages</h3>
        <p>English (Fluent), Tamil (Native)</p>
        <a href="/resume.pdf" class="btn btn-blue" target="_blank">[ download resume ]</a>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .main-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 8rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .inline-nav {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cmd-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  
  .cmd-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .page-transition {
    animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Typography overrides for prose */
  .prose {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose h3 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .prose ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .prose li::before {
    content: '- ';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-blue);
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
